title: Conversations in New York: Jimmy Heath and Phil Woods with Gary Smulyan - Chapter One -

description:
In this installment of Vandoren's interview series, "Conversations in New York," jazz icons Jimmy Heath and Phil Woods sit down for an exclusive interview with Gary Smulyan.

In chapter one of this six-part video conversation, Jimmy Heath and Phil Woods discuss their early mentors, playing the saxophone as kids, and their musical upbringings. Stay posted for the following five chapters, to be released each following Thursday.
